                                        <property name="visible">True</property>
                                        <property name="can-focus">True</property>
                                        <property name="halign">start</property>
                                        <property name="label" translatable="yes">You can now actively watch individual folders to eliminate frequent rescans. File changes then appear in your search results immediately.

To enable this feature go to the Database section of the Preferences dialog.

See the online documentation for more information:
&lt;a href="URL"&gt;https://github.com/cboxdoerfer/fsearch/wiki/Database-update&lt;/a&gt;</property>
